   Logo for the E-Marketplace: BuyUSA

   The Commercial Service has a human resource network that spans the
   globe. Our export and industry specialists are located in more than 80
   cities across the United States to assist small and midsized US
   businesses export their products and services, and in more than 80
   countries to assist foreign buyers.

   To best address your issue or inquiry, please select one of the
   following communication methods:

   Note: For general questions about exporting such as tariff rates or
   U.S. Federal Government export asistance programs, we encourage you to
   call the Trade Information Center at 1-800-USATRAD(E), or use the
   Exporter's Toolkit located in this website.

   Contact a Trade Specialist Near You

   US Sellers: Use the following menu to local an Export Assistance Center
   near you.

